sections.heading: payments for street purposes; priority
sections.text: Before distributing the February portion of funds under sections 39-2518 and 66-4,148, incentive payments shall first be made as provided in sections 39-2512 to 39-2515.SourceLaws 1969, c. 316, ยง 1, p. 1139;Laws 2001, LB 142, ยง 45;Laws 2021, LB174, ยง 17.
